urls.description: Wonhan, a berserker of the wastes, has encountered a sinister deceiver which now takes on the image of her departed mother. The once warm memories that have given Wonhan strength and the will to survive the harsh forbidden lands are being warped and used against her. Driven to despair and backed into a corner, Wonhan must find a new way to rely upon herself and overcome the deceiver's onslaught.
urls.title: The Winner's Smile
